sequenceDiagram
    participant U as User
    participant UI as React UI
    participant H as useStream Hook
    participant S as LangGraph Server
    participant A as Agent Runtime

    U->>UI: 메시지 입력
    UI->>H: submit(messages)
    H->>S: POST /runs + stream 연결
    S->>A: 그래프 실행 시작
    A-->>S: on_chat_model_start
    S-->>H: start event
    H-->>UI: 로딩 상태 표시
    A-->>S: on_chat_model_stream
    S-->>H: token chunk
    H-->>UI: 부분 응답 렌더링
    A-->>S: on_tool_start / on_tool_end
    S-->>H: tool events
    H-->>UI: 진행 상태 / 스피너 갱신
    A-->>S: final state
    S-->>H: completed event
    H-->>UI: 메시지 확정 저장
